				<wikidot:authorName>Bassoe</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>3070028</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>While in general I like it, I don't approve of the pictures. Specifically, the first drawing of Agent Briggs' mutated hand being a <em>drawing</em> rather than a public-domain photograph of an actual bird's claw (possibly <a href="https://www.ancient-origins.net/history/mount-owen-claw-003696?">a mummified moa claw</a>, though I'm unsure about the copyright status) and the second picture of Agent Briggs' forearm-turned-wing being a wing, showing no signs of the avian claw hand described in the text.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
